 * SpiderMonkey wrapper to compress Javascript source files,
 * uses Dean Edwards (http://dean.edwards.name/packer/)
 *
 * Author: Diego Perini <diego.perini@gmail.com>
 *
 * Usage: fusecomp.js < input > output (uses stdin/stdout)
